dashboardQueries.name: 9185ab07-1c2c-41cb-b1b2-76f02b2f3856
35a5ef85-aa0c-4c34-89df-b64542e85fc4
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type = "corelight_metrics_iface"
$date_hour=timestamp.get_timestamp(metadata.event_timestamp.seconds, "%Y-%m-%d : %H")
$rate_name=if(about.labels.key="mgmt_in_packets_kpps", "Inbound Traffic Packet Rate", 
      if(about.labels.key="mgmt_out_packets_kpps", "Outbound Traffic Packet Rate", "Unknown"))
$rate_name!="Unknown"
match:
    $date_hour, $rate_name
outcome:
    $avg_rate=math.round(window.avg(cast.as_float(about.labels.value)), 3)
order:
    $date_hour asc

dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type = "corelight_metrics_bro"
$date_hour=timestamp.get_timestamp(metadata.event_timestamp.seconds, "%Y-%m-%d : %H")
$files=if(about.labels.key="files_total", "Extracted Files", 
       if(about.labels.key="files_queued_sftp", "Queued Files for SFTP", 
       if(about.labels.key="files_queued_s3", "Queued Files for Amazon S3", "Unknown")))
$files!="Unknown"
match:
    $date_hour, $files
outcome:
    $files_avg=math.round(window.avg(cast.as_float(about.labels.value)), 3)
order:
    $date_hour asc
